同下到公園，「未見過（貓頭鷹），淨係喺新聞見過，今日未見到」。<br />\n<br />\n攝影發燒友盧先生，之前從未拍攝過貓頭鷹，今早7時便到公園等候貓頭鷹BB現身攝入鏡頭，直至中午「見到有5隻，但只係影到3隻半」，會一直在現場等候直至體力支持不住為止，就算「落雨都唔會走」。　<br />\n<br />\n康文署職員已即時將附近一帶圍封，以免野生雀鳥受到滋擾，漁護署發言人回應，過去數天晚上都有派人到上述公園視察貓頭鷹的情況，有需要時向龍友作出勸喻，指其中兩隻貓頭鷹BB羽翼已漸長，牠們是因學飛而到達地面，愛護動物協會發言人指，應宜保持10米距離觀賞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180507/58161392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180507%2F58161392&d=4tRPLw2x%2Bopihp7tnb4LpTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=f4c8c895\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180507%2F58161392&h=f57cdaaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180507/58161392</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180507/large/1525657156_bb3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180507%2Flarge%2F1525657156_bb3d.jpg&h=4a40b966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180507/large/1525668628_aeb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180507%2Flarge%2F1525668628_aeb7.jpg&h=56a4f0da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180507/large/1525669644_0745.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180507%2Flarge%2F1525669644_0745.jpg&h=dd08f816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n貓頭鷹: 屌你老母，返去照你老母西"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T00:46:12.000Z","msg":"發現新大陸乎？"},{"pid":"d4dbc179997d93313fef1dc3b29225d43b6720a0","tid":656403,"uid":61922,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T00:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f17b